# Third-party notices — `eig_lapack_nobalance` (Option B)

## LAPACK (Netlib)

This experiment may vendor a **minimal subset** of LAPACK reference Fortran sources
required for real double-precision `DGEEVX` with `BALANC='N'`.

- **Upstream:** https://www.netlib.org/lapack/
- **Target version for B1 extract:** **3.12.0** (document exact tag in `SOURCES.md` when extracted)
