## BLAS (link-time only for prototype)

The native library is intended to link against **existing** BLAS on the build
machine (OpenBLAS as used by NumPy/SciPy on `rgms` for prototypes). BLAS is
**not** vendored in B1 unless explicitly added later with separate notices.

